FERMENTATION CONTROLLER:
1. Upload get_temp/get_temp.ino to arduino.
2. %> python ferm_chamber_controller.py --brew_name <brew name> --set_temp <temp> --set_range <range> --{cool|heat|dual_stage}

EKETTLE CONTROLLER:
%> python ekettle_controller.py --brew_name <brew name> --set_temp <temp> --set_range <range>
To find ip of raspberry pi:
%> arp -a //then try all these with pi@<ip>

WEBSITE:

To start ssh:
%> ssh-agent /bin/bash

Server:

Initial setup:
 %> sudo apt-get install python-flask
To run:
 %> cd server/
 %> . venv/bin/activate
 %>  python brew_server.py
Runs on: http://127.0.0.1:5000/
